---
title: Charred Corn and Jalapeño Beyond Meat® Tacos with Sour Cream and Cheddar
description: Charred corn, jalapeños and chipotle sauce add layers of delicious, spicy smokiness to these Beyond Meat® tacos. A sprinkling of cheddar and a refreshing crunch from the cabbage provides some respite from the mild heat!
